title: Cyberpunk Music Pack 2
description: This is a music pack featuring fifteen unique cyberpunk instrumental tracks utilizing orchestral and ambient effects, which are versatile enough to use across a wide variety of projects.
longDescription:
Music composer, Living Force is proud to present Cyberpunk Music Pack 2! This is an asset pack that contains fifteen orchestral/ambient fused instrumentals geared towards the world of Cyberpunk. The pieces all contain a fade-out and are loopable for desired cut scenes, action sequences, and transitions for your projects.


Cascade - Eb Minor - 110 BPM

Encounter - E Minor - 80 BPM

Ocean - Life - F Minor - 70 BPM

Most Wanted - F Minor - 70 BPM

Precious - Cargo - A Major - 80 BPM

East Side C Minor 82BPM

The Cellar -C - Minor 90 BPM

Melancholy - C Minor - 95 BPM

Paradise Lost - C Minor - 70 BPM

Point Of Return - C Minor - 120 BPM

Remember - C Minor - 128 BPM

Rites Of Passage - C Minor - 90 BPM

Solitude - D Minor - 150 BPM

The Clock - E Major -100 BPM

Wander My Friends - C Minor - 90 BPM
